title: Sam Darnold Interview, Sean Wagner on Dolphins anthem and backpacks (Football 07/20)
description:
Will Brinson is joined by Sean Wagner to break down the latest NFL news (and non NFL news), including whether or not it's acceptable for a man in his mid 30's to wear a backpack instead of a professional bag of some kind, if Roquan Smith should get his own Rogue One cover, the Dolphins anthem decision and Danny Amendola calling Bill Belichick "a principal." Then New York Jets quarterback Sam Darnold joins the show to lay out his situation heading into the season.
​
